<p><strong>Senses</strong> darkvision 30 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Variant: Hold Breath.</em></strong> The lizard can hold its breath for 15 minutes. (A lizard that has this trait also has a swimming speed of 30 feet.)</p>

<p><strong><em>Variant: Spider Climb.</em></strong> The lizard can climb difficult surfaces, including upside down on ceilings, without needing to make an ability check.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

